<section class="material-section">
  <div class="material-inner">

    <div class="material-header reveal">
      <span class="section-label">The Stone</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Why <span class="section-title-accent">Amethyst?</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="material-grid">

      <article class="material-card material-card--hero reveal">
        <span class="material-hero-label">The material</span>
        <h3 class="material-hero-title">Not all stones are equal.</h3>
        <p class="material-hero-text">Most gua sha sold online is Xiuyan jade, nephrite, or dyed glass &mdash; cheap materials that polish unevenly and leave micro-ridges that drag across skin. Amethyst sits at 7 on the Mohs scale: harder than nephrite jade, smoother after finishing, and naturally cool to the touch without refrigeration.</p>
        <p class="material-hero-stat"><span>7 Mohs hardness</span><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span><span>Hand-finished</span></p>
      </article>

      <article class="material-card material-card--proof reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="material-card-num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <h4 class="material-card-subtitle">Feels cool on skin</h4>
        <p class="material-card-text">Natural crystal stays cool without refrigeration &mdash; a soothing start to the morning.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="material-card material-card--proof reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="material-card-num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <h4 class="material-card-subtitle">Smoother polish</h4>
        <p class="material-card-text">Harder than jade on the Mohs scale, so it finishes smoother. Better glide with oil, no micro-scratches.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="material-card material-card--proof reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <span class="material-card-num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <h4 class="material-card-subtitle">Each stone is unique</h4>
        <p class="material-card-text">Natural colour variation means no two are alike. The one you receive is the one shown in your photos.</p>
      </article>

    </div>

    <div class="material-comparison reveal" role="table" aria-label="Comparison of BY RITUEL amethyst gua sha against generic gua sha">
      <div class="material-compare-row material-compare-header" role="row">
        <span role="columnheader"></span>
        <span class="compare-brand" role="columnheader">BY RITUEL Amethyst</span>
        <span class="compare-generic" role="columnheader">Generic Gua Sha</span>
      </div>
      <div class="material-compare-row" role="row">
        <span class="compare-feature" role="rowheader">Material</span>
        <span class="compare-good" role="cell">Genuine amethyst crystal</span>
        <span class="compare-bad" role="cell">Xiuyan jade or dyed glass</span>
      </div>
      <div class="material-compare-row" role="row">
        <span class="compare-feature" role="rowheader">Hardness</span>
        <span class="compare-good" role="cell">7 Mohs &mdash; harder than nephrite jade</span>
        <span class="compare-bad" role="cell">Varies &mdash; often softer, can chip</span>
      </div>
      <div class="material-compare-row" role="row">
        <span class="compare-feature" role="rowheader">Surface polish</span>
        <span class="compare-good" role="cell">Ultra-smooth finish</span>
        <span class="compare-bad" role="cell">Rough or uneven edges</span>
      </div>
      <div class="material-compare-row" role="row">
        <span class="compare-feature" role="rowheader">Edge design</span>
        <span class="compare-good" role="cell">Concave jawline edge</span>
        <span class="compare-bad" role="cell">Generic flat shape</span>
      </div>
      <div class="material-compare-row" role="row">
        <span class="compare-feature" role="rowheader">Includes guide</span>
        <span class="compare-good" role="cell">Step-by-step ritual card</span>
        <span class="compare-bad" role="cell">No instructions</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .material-section {
    padding: 112px 80px;
    background: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
    color: var(--cream, #F7F2EA);
  }
  .material-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .material-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  .material-header .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .material-header .section-title {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--cream, #F7F2EA);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .section-title-accent {
    color: var(--blush, #E8C5B0);
  }

  .material-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.55fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: repeat(3, auto);
    gap: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .material-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
    padding: 44px 36px;
  }

  .material-card--hero {
    grid-column: 1;
    grid-row: 1 / 4;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 56px 48px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }
  .material-hero-label {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .material-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 2.6vw, 34px);
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--cream, #F7F2EA);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .material-hero-text {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.78);
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }
  .material-hero-stat {
    margin: auto 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blush, #E8C5B0);
  }
  .material-hero-stat .dot {
    opacity: 0.45;
  }

  .material-card--proof {
    grid-column: 2;
  }
  .material-card-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    color: var(--blush, #E8C5B0);
    opacity: 0.22;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .material-card-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blush, #E8C5B0);
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  .material-card-text {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.72);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Comparison table */
  .material-comparison {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .material-compare-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr 1.2fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.08);
  }
  .material-compare-header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.18);
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .compare-brand,
  .compare-generic {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 14px 18px;
  }
  .compare-brand {
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
  }
  .compare-generic {
    color: rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.50);
  }
  .compare-feature {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream, #F7F2EA);
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .compare-good,
  .compare-bad {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .compare-good {
    color: rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.82);
  }
  .compare-bad {
    color: rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.50);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .material-section {
      padding: 72px 24px;
    }
    .material-header {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .material-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto;
      gap: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }
    .material-card--hero {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: auto;
      padding: 40px 28px;
    }
    .material-card--proof {
      grid-column: 1;
      padding: 32px 28px;
    }

    .material-comparison {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    .material-compare-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 14px 0;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .material-compare-header {
      display: none;
    }
    .compare-feature {
      padding: 0 2px 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--blush, #E8C5B0);
    }
    .compare-good,
    .compare-bad {
      padding: 2px 2px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .compare-good::before {
      content: "BY RITUEL \00a0\00b7\00a0 ";
      color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .compare-bad::before {
      content: "Generic \00a0\00b7\00a0 ";
      color: rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.50);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .material-card,
    .material-card--hero {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Material Education",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Material Education" }]
}
{% endschema %}
